movies.title: I, Tonya
movies.plot: Competitive ice skater Tonya Harding rises amongst the ranks at the U.S. Figure Skating Championships, but her future in the activity is thrown into doubt when her ex-husband intervenes.

movies.title: Apollo 11
movies.plot: A look at the Apollo 11 mission to land on the moon led by commander Neil Armstrong and pilots Buzz Aldrin and Michael Collins.
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 52 wins & 35 nominations.
